Pitfall ID: P07
Pitfall Name: Merging different concepts in the same class
Pitfall Description: A class whose name refers to two or more different concepts is created.
Affected Element: http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#TrainingAndOnboarding

### Ontology context (Turtle)
```turtle
@prefix : <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/fsl#> .
@prefix ae: <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ae#> .
@prefix ce: <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#> .
@prefix fe: <http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/fe#> .
